#eNCA​ Lindokuhle Xulu brings us the latest update. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The four police officers accused of killing Mthokozisi Ntumba made their first appearance at the Johannesburg Magistrate's Court. Their bail application has been set for 24 March. READ: Four police officers to appear in court over Ntumba's killing The officers face charges of murder, three charges of attempted murder and defeating the ends of justice. Ntumba was shot dead when police were dispersing protesting students last week. Watch the video above for more on this story. The four police officers accused of killing Mthokozisi Ntumba have made their first appearance at the Johannesburg Magistrate's Court. Their bail application is set for 24 March #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403